---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---
<Layout title="Custom MQL5 EA & Indicator Programming | VerifiedPropFirm" description="Professional custom Expert Advisor (EA) and MQL5 indicator development. Starting from $30 USD. If your strategy can be expressed in logic, we can automate it.">
  <script src="https://challenges.cloudflare.com/turnstile/v0/api.js" async defer slot="head"></script>
  <script type="application/ld+json" slot="head">
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@graph":[
      {
        "@type": "Service",
        "serviceType": "Custom MQL5 EA Development",
        "provider": {
          "@type": "Organization",
          "name": "VerifiedPropFirm",
          "url": "https://verifiedpropfirm.com"
        },
        "areaServed": "Worldwide",
        "offers": {
          "@type": "Offer",
          "price": "30.00",
          "priceCurrency": "USD",
          "description": "Starting price for basic indicator modifications or utility scripts."
        },
        "description": "Professional custom Expert Advisor (EA) and MQL5 indicator programming tailored for proprietary trading firms and retail brokers."
      },
      {
        "@type": "FAQPage",
        "mainEntity":[
          {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "Will I receive the source code (.mq5 file)?",
            "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Yes. By default, we deliver the compiled .ex5 file. However, the fully open-source, commented .mq5 file is always available for a small additional fee." }
          },
          {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "Can you code an EA specifically for prop firm rules?",
            "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Absolutely. We specialize in building EAs with built-in daily drawdown monitors, equity protectors, and news-filter utilities to ensure you never accidentally breach a prop firm's strict rules." }
          },
          {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "How long does custom EA development take?",
            "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Simple utility scripts or indicator modifications usually take 2 to 4 days. Full-scale automated trading systems with complex multi-timeframe logic typically take 1 to 2 weeks." }
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  }
  </script>
  <div class="min-h-screen bg-slate-950 text-slate-50 font-sans">
    <Header />
    <main class="py-20 pb-16">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-16 relative">
          <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-3/4 h-48 bg-blue-600/20 blur-[100px] -z-10 rounded-full"></div>
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-blue-500/10 text-blue-400 text-sm font-semibold mb-6 border border-blue-500/20">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="4 17 10 11 4 5"/><line x1="12" x2="20" y1="19" y2="19"/></svg>
            Professional Development
          </div>
          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 tracking-tight">Custom <span class="text-gradient">MQL5 EAs & Indicators</span></h1>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">Automate your edge. We build bespoke Expert Advisors (EAs) and custom indicators.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-16">
          <div class="bg-slate-900/50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 shadow-lg group hover:border-blue-500/30 transition-colors">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-blue-500/10 border border-blue-500/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-blue-400 shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(59,130,246,0.1)] group-hover:bg-blue-500/20 transition-colors">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 8V4H8"/><rect width="16" height="12" x="4" y="8" rx="2"/><path d="M2 14h2"/><path d="M20 14h2"/><path d="M15 13v2"/><path d="M9 13v2"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Limitless Automation</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">If your trading strategy can be expressed in a clear logic, we can automate it. We can turn any mechanical system into a fully functional EA.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-slate-900/50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 shadow-lg group hover:border-indigo-500/30 transition-colors">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-indigo-500/10 border border-indigo-500/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-indigo-400 shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(99,102,241,0.1)] group-hover:bg-indigo-500/20 transition-colors">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m13 2-2 10h3L10 22l2-10H9l4-10z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">High-Speed Execution</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">Optimized MQL5 architecture ensures your algorithms react to market conditions instantly with minimal latency.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-slate-900/50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 shadow-lg group hover:border-emerald-500/30 transition-colors">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-emerald-500/10 border border-emerald-500/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-emerald-400 shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(16,185,129,0.1)] group-hover:bg-emerald-500/20 transition-colors">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="12" x2="12" y1="2" y2="22"/><path d="M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Highly Affordable</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">Professional algorithmic trading shouldn't break the bank. Our custom programming services are extremely accessible, with pricing starting from just $30 USD.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* Portfolio Section */}
        <div class="mb-20">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-10 text-center">Examples of What We Can Build</h2>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <div class="bg-slate-900/50 border border-slate-800 rounded-2xl p-6 hover:border-blue-500/30 transition-all group">
              <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-2 py-0.5 rounded bg-blue-500/10 text-blue-400 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider mb-4 border border-blue-500/20">
                Risk Management
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3 group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">The Prop Firm Equity Guardian</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
                A custom utility designed to monitor your MT5 account equity in real-time. If floating drawdown approaches the firm's 4% daily limit, the EA instantly liquidates all positions and disables auto-trading until midnight.
              </p>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-auto">
                <span class="text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-500 bg-slate-800 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">Utility</span>
                <span class="text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-500 bg-slate-800 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">Prop Firm Safe</span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-slate-900/50 border border-slate-800 rounded-2xl p-6 hover:border-indigo-500/30 transition-all group">
              <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-2 py-0.5 rounded bg-indigo-500/10 text-indigo-400 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider mb-4 border border-indigo-500/20">
                Full Automation
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3 group-hover:text-indigo-400 transition-colors">Automated Gold Scalper</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
                A high-frequency mechanical EA that trades XAUUSD using a combination of RSI divergence on the M5 timeframe and ATR-based dynamic stop losses. Includes stealth/virtual stop losses to hide levels from B-book brokers.
              </p>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-auto">
                <span class="text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-500 bg-slate-800 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">Algorithmic</span>
                <span class="text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-500 bg-slate-800 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">Stealth</span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-slate-900/50 border border-slate-800 rounded-2xl p-6 hover:border-emerald-500/30 transition-all group">
              <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-2 py-0.5 rounded bg-emerald-500/10 text-emerald-400 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider mb-4 border border-emerald-500/20">
                API Integration
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3 group-hover:text-emerald-400 transition-colors">Automated News Filter</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
                An EA add-on that connects to the ForexFactory calendar API. It automatically pauses all your other running EAs 15 minutes before red-folder high-impact news events (like NFP or CPI) and resumes them 15 minutes after.
              </p>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-auto">
                <span class="text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-500 bg-slate-800 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">News Trading</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-900 rounded-3xl border border-slate-800 p-8 md:p-12 mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-8 text-center">The Development Process</h2>
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div class="flex gap-4"><div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-blue-600 flex items-center justify-center font-bold">1</div><div><h4 class="text-lg font-bold mb-1">Requirement Gathering</h4><p class="text-slate-400 text-sm">You provide the exact logic, entry/exit parameters, and risk management rules for your strategy.</p></div></div>
            <div class="flex gap-4"><div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-blue-600 flex items-center justify-center font-bold">2</div><div><h4 class="text-lg font-bold mb-1">Development & Backtesting</h4><p class="text-slate-400 text-sm">We code the algorithm in MQL5 and run preliminary historical backtests to ensure technical stability.</p></div></div>
            <div class="flex gap-4"><div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-blue-600 flex items-center justify-center font-bold">3</div><div><h4 class="text-lg font-bold mb-1">Delivery & Revisions</h4><p class="text-slate-400 text-sm">You receive the compiled .ex5 file (or source code) and we provide revisions to ensure the EA behaves exactly as requested.</p></div></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          <div class="text-center mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Request a Quote</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-400">Describe your strategy in detail. We will review your requirements and get back to you with a development timeline and price estimate.</p>
          </div>
          <div id="service-container" class="bg-slate-900/80 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 shadow-xl">
            <form id="service-form" action="https://verifiedpropfirm.com/submit" method="POST" class="space-y-6">
              <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="service-request" />
              <input type="hidden" name="_subject" value="New MQL5 Development Request!" />
              <input type="hidden" name="_template" value="table" />
              <input type="hidden" name="_captcha" value="false" />
              <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                <div><label class="block text-sm font-medium text-slate-300 mb-2">Name</label><input type="text" name="name" required class="w-full bg-slate-950 border border-slate-800 rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-slate-50 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 transition-all" placeholder="John Doe" /></div>
                <div><label class="block text-sm font-medium text-slate-300 mb-2">Email</label><input type="email" name="email" required class="w-full bg-slate-950 border border-slate-800 rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-slate-50 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 transition-all" placeholder="john@example.com" /></div>
              </div>
              <div><label class="block text-sm font-medium text-slate-300 mb-2">Project Type</label><select name="project_type" class="w-full bg-slate-950 border border-slate-800 rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-slate-50 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 transition-all"><option value="Expert Advisor (EA)">Expert Advisor (EA)</option><option value="Custom Indicator">Custom Indicator</option><option value="Trade Management Panel">Trade Management Panel</option><option value="Other">Other</option></select></div>
              <div><label class="block text-sm font-medium text-slate-300 mb-2">Strategy Details</label><textarea name="details" required rows="6" class="w-full bg-slate-950 border border-slate-800 rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-slate-50 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 transition-all" placeholder="Please describe your entry rules, exit rules, risk management, and the platforms/firms you intend to use this on..."></textarea></div>
              
              <!-- Cloudflare Turnstile -->
              <div class="cf-turnstile py-2" data-sitekey="0x4AAAAAADMraoaqaakRPjqQ" data-theme="dark"></div>

              <button type="submit" class="w-full premium-button bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-500 text-white font-bold py-4 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center gap-3 transition-all">
                <span id="service-button-text">Submit Project Request →</span>
                <span id="service-loading" class="hidden">
                  <svg class="animate-spin h-5 w-5 text-white" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <circle class="opacity-25" cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="4"></circle>
                    <path class="opacity-75" fill="currentColor" d="M4 12a8 8 0 018-8V0C5.373 0 0 5.373 0 12h4zm2 5.291A7.962 7.962 0 014 12H0c0 3.042 1.135 5.824 3 7.938l3-2.647z"></path>
                  </svg>
                </span>
              </button>
            </form>

            <div id="service-success" class="hidden text-center py-12 animate-fade-in">
              <div class="w-24 h-24 bg-blue-600/20 text-blue-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 shadow-[0_0_40px_rgba(37,99,235,0.1)]">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="16 16 12 12 8 16"></polyline><line x1="12" y1="12" x2="12" y2="21"></line><path d="M20.39 18.39A5 5 0 0 0 18 9h-1.26A8 8 0 1 0 3 16.3"></path><polyline points="16 16 12 12 8 16"></polyline></svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Request Received!</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-400 max-w-sm mx-auto leading-relaxed text-lg">
                Your strategy details have been submitted. We'll analyze your requirements and reach out via email with a quote and timeline within 48 hours.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <script is:inline>
            const sForm = document.getElementById('service-form');
            const sSuccess = document.getElementById('service-success');
            const sBtnText = document.getElementById('service-button-text');
            const sLoading = document.getElementById('service-loading');

            if (sForm) {
              sForm.addEventListener('submit', async (e) => {
                e.preventDefault();
                
                sBtnText.classList.add('hidden');
                sLoading.classList.remove('hidden');
                sForm.style.opacity = '0.5';
                sForm.style.pointerEvents = 'none';

                const formData = new FormData(sForm);
                const data = {
                  form_name: "MQL5 Service Request",
                  name: formData.get('name'),
                  email: formData.get('email'),
                  project_type: formData.get('project_type'),
                  details: formData.get('details')
                };
                
                try {
                  const response = await fetch(sForm.action, {
                    method: 'POST',
                    body: JSON.stringify(data),
                    headers: { 
                      'Content-Type': 'application/json',
                      'Accept': 'application/json' 
                    }
                  });

                  const result = await response.json();

                  if (response.ok || result.success) {
                    sForm.classList.add('hidden');
                    sSuccess.classList.remove('hidden');
                  } else {
                    throw new Error('Failed');
                  }
                } catch (error) {
                  alert('Request failed. Please check your connection or email us directly.');
                  sForm.style.opacity = '1';
                  sForm.style.pointerEvents = 'auto';
                  sBtnText.classList.remove('hidden');
                  sLoading.classList.add('hidden');
                }
              });
            }
          </script>

          {/* FAQ Section */}
          <div class="mt-24 border-t border-slate-800 pt-16">
            <div class="text-center mb-12">
              <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Frequently Asked Questions (Custom Programming)</h2>
              <p class="text-slate-400">Everything you need to know about our custom MQL5 development services.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-6">
              <div class="bg-slate-900/50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-800">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Will I receive the source code (.mq5 or .mq4 file)?</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">Yes. By default, we deliver the compiled, ready-to-trade executable file (.ex4 / .ex5). However, if you want full ownership of the intellectual property, the fully commented open-source file is available for an agreed-upon additional fee.</p>
              </div>

              <div class="bg-slate-900/50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-800">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Can you code an EA specifically for prop firm rules?</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">Absolutely. Because we are prop firm traders ourselves, we understand the nuances. We specialize in building EAs with built-in daily drawdown monitors, weekend-close functions, and news-filter utilities to ensure you never accidentally breach a rule.</p>
              </div>

              <div class="bg-slate-900/50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-800">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">How long does custom EA development take?</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">Simple utility scripts or indicator alerts usually take 2 to 4 days. Full-scale automated trading systems with complex multi-timeframe logic and risk algorithms typically take 1 to 2 weeks, including initial backtesting.</p>
              </div>

              <div class="bg-slate-900/50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-800">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">What if there is a bug in the code?</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">We offer a 30-day bug-fixing guarantee. If the EA does not execute exactly according to the logic you provided in your initial requirements, we will revise and fix the code at no extra charge.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </div>
</Layout>
